(35, 1, '2021-09-22 22:07:49', '2021-09-22 22:07:49', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Ghi bn: c Huy 18, c Ho 39 - Robinho 11, Chishkala 18, 30</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nm nm trc ti Colombia, Nga thng Vit Nam ti 7-0 cng  vng 1/8 futsal World Cup, nhng ln ny tnh th  thay i.  Vilnius ti 22/9, Nga khng c lc no to c cch bit ba bn trc Vit Nam. Thy tr Phm Minh Giang thm ch ghi c hai bn nh cng ca pivot Nguyn c Huy v hu v Phm c Ho. Nhng, Nga vn i tip vo t kt nh bn thng ca Robinho v c p cho Ivan Chishkala.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/09/22/da-c-huy-jpeg-1632328254-5170-1632328316.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=6Ba7xTBALBjafsR5w4ziVw\" alt=\"c Huy (phi) mng bn sau khi nh u ni t ng chuyn bng u ca Gia Hng (tri). nh: VFF\"/><figcaption>c Huy (phi) mng bn sau khi nh u ni t ng chuyn bng u ca Gia Hng (tri). nh:&nbsp;<em>VFF</em></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khng bt ng khi Vit Nam chn li chi phng ng phn cng quen thuc, khi i ch gi bng 28% thi lng hip mt. on qun ca Minh Giang ng vng trong 10 pht u tin, nh vo t nht nm pha cu thua p mt ca th mn H Vn . Anh lin tc bay ngi, chui xung, vn tay ph bng hay thm ch dng thn mnh  ngn c st ca i phng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>n pht 11, Nga bt ng thay i chin thut, bng cch cm ba cu th vo cm a Vit Nam v  Robinho cm bng qua ngi. Tin v 38 tui gc Brazil vt qua Vn Ho bn phi, chuyn vo cho Afanasev lm tng. Lc ny th mn Vn  phi lao ra  lm hp gc st, nhng Afanasev li gt sang cho Robinho m vo khung thnh trng  m t s.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/09/22/hoa-jpeg-1632328178-1632328196-9087-1632328316.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=qJ_yq9Bx9r38FLAdxsJ15g\" alt=\"Tnh hung Robinho (tri) vt qua c Ho trc khi ghi bn. nh: VFF\"/><figcaption>Tnh hung Robinho (tri) vt qua c Ho trc khi ghi bn. nh:&nbsp;<em>VFF</em></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Robinho sau khi ghi bn, ra sn ngh vi pht. Sau khi tr li, anh  bin cho Chishkala st mt chm a bng i qua hai chn th mn Vn , ri ln vo li. Nga dn 2-0 khi hip mt ch cn hai pht. Hai cu th ny c coi l cp bi trng ca Nga, khi cng chi cho CLB Benfica  B o Nha.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhng th dn hai bn ca Nga ch tn ti vi giy, khi Vit Nam rt ngn t s chng vnh. Th mn Vn  chuyn di ln cho Gia Hng nh u vo cm a. c Huy p vo nh u ni cn thnh h gc th mn Putilov. Sau khi ghi bn, c Huy gi o s 10 ca pivot Nguyn c Tng ln,  tri n cu th ny b chn thng u gi nng t trn cui vng bng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nga khng chp nhn thng cch bit mt bn, m dn ln tn cng u hip hai. Sau khi Artem Niyazov v Sergei Abramov st trng ct dc lin tip, on qun ca HLV Sergey Skorovich cng ghi c bn th ba. Li l Robinho chuyn bng  Chishkala x l ngoi cm a. Chishkala r bng xung bin tri, vt qua Minh Tr, ri st chm cho gc h gc th mn Vn . y l bn th nm ca anh ti gii, cn Robinho c tnh hung th tm ghi du giy vo bn thng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhng, Vit Nam vn khng nn ch  tm bn g thm. Sau khi tin v tr Nguyn Vn Hiu m bng chch ct, Vit Nam chuyn sang chi power-play. T mt tnh hung nh th  pht 39, i trng Trn Vn V cp bng trong chn Ivan Milovanov ngay ra cm a Nga. c Ho ng ngay cnh, thc mi giy a bng i cng v tung li Nga, khi th mn Dmitri Putilov khng kp tr tay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/09/22/duc-hoa-jpeg-7043-1632329313.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=CkKk4i9PRTWjWJiTJDAD5w\" alt=\"Vit Nam (o ) dng bc  vng 1/8, ln th hai lin tip. nh: VFF\"/><figcaption>Vit Nam (o ) dng bc  vng 1/8, ln th hai lin tip. nh:&nbsp;<em>VFF</em></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vi cch bit ch cn mt bn, Vit Nam tt tay  tm bn g ho nhm a trn u vo hip ph. Nhng, c hi cui ca Minh Tr khng th thnh bn, khi anh st t gc hp sut qua c hai chn th mn Nga.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trn thua st nt 2-3 cng l kt qu nm ngoi d on, cho thy Vit Nam phn no  tin b so vi ln u d futsal World Cup nm 2016. T s ny cng l bt ng khi Nga ang hn Vit Nam 35 bc th gii. Nga s vo t kt gp ng kim v ch Argentina hoc Paraguay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Vit Nam thua st Nga  vng 1/8 futsal World Cup', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-09-22 22:07:49', '2021-09-22 22:07:49', '', 1, 'http://localhost/wordpress_581/?p=35', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(36, 1, '2021-09-22 22:09:49', '2021-09-22 22:09:49', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ANHDng i hnh hai v khng ng k siu sao Cristiano Ronaldo, Man Utd thua i khch West Ham 0-1  vng ba Cup Lin on ti 22/9.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Ghi bn: Lanzini 9</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi trn u ch cn tnh bng giy v Man Utd b dn 0-1, HLV Ole Gunnar Solskjaer vn ci a vi ng nghip David Moyes sau mt tnh hung trn sn. Man Utd b loi khi Cup Lin on, khin h mt thm mt c hi chm dt chui nm nm trng tay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tung ra sn i hnh hai khin Man Utd sm thng li. Pht th chn, hu v phi Ryan Fredericks bt ng dc bng vt qua Alex Telles, ri chuyn ngc ra cho Manuel Lanzini m bng st v gc xa. West Ham li dn trc ging nh cuc i u gia hai i  Ngoi hng Anh hm 19/9.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/09/23/man-utd-jpeg-1632341093-5239-1632341394.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=69njs_PCX-QZsiIyrIhCMg\" alt=\"Man Utd (o ) nhp cuc khng tt v sm b dn trc. nh: REX\"/><figcaption>Man Utd (o ) nhp cuc khng tt v sm b dn trc. nh:&nbsp;<em>REX</em></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bn thua ny khin Man Utd phi y cao tc , v to ra vi c hi. ng k l tnh hung trng ti Jon Moss t chi pht n cho Man Utd, khi Mark Noble ko ng Jesse Lingard trong cm a. Khng lu sau, Juan Mata st di x ngang sau tnh hung lp bp trong cm a. Ch nh dt im 13 qu trong hip mt, hn gp ba ln so vi West Ham.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Solskjaer phi a cc cu th chnh thc vo sn  hip hai, u tin l Mason Greenwood  pht 62. Ch sau hn 10 giy trn sn, Greenwood c c hi i mt sau ng chuyn ca Donny van de Beek ra sau hng th West Ham. Nhng Greenwood st khng trng tm bng, b th mn Alphonse Areola dng chn ph.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mi pht sau, n lt Bruno Fernandes v tin v tr Anthony Elanga vo sn, nhng khng to c du n. Man Utd vn c thm vi c hi nhng phung ph. Pht 81, t c st xa ca Jadon Sancho, bng i hng gip Anthony Martial i mt th mn. Nhng, trong ngy chi xut thn, th mn Areola lao ra kp thi  chn c st ca Martial.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Solskjaer khng ng k Cristiano Ronaldo, Paul Pogba hay Harry Maguire cho trn ny, khin Man Utd cng ht phng n thay i nhn s. H thm ch sut thng thm bn  pht 86, khi Yarmolenko st trng ct dc sau mt pha phn cng. Hai pht sau, n lt i trng Noble b l c hi i mt thun li cng t pha bng hai nh mt.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Man Utd ch cn chi  ba u trng ma ny, gm Ngoi hng Anh, Cup FA v Champions League, trong  Cup FA bt u thi u t u nm 2022.  trn tip theo, Man Utd tip Aston Villa trn sn Old Trafford  vng su Ngoi hng Anh th by 25/9.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Danh sch thi u</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Man Utd</em>: Henderson, Dalot, Lindelof, Bailly, Alex Telles (Elanga 72), Mata (Greenwood 62), Matic, van de Beek, Sancho, Martial, Lingard (Fernandes 72).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>West Ham</em>: Areola, Johnson, Dawson, Diop, Fredericks (Coufal 17), Noble, Kral, Yarmolenko, Lanzini (Fornals 69), Masuaku (Vlasic 69), Bowen.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Man Utd b loi khi Cup Lin on', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-09-22 22:09:49', '2021-09-22 22:09:49', '', 10, 'http://localhost/wordpress_581/?p=36', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(37, 1, '2021-09-22 22:10:32', '2021-09-22 22:10:32', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HLV Ole Solskjaer bc b lun im ca cu trung v Rio Ferdinand v vic Cristiano Ronaldo ng ngoi ng bin h ho trong trn u Young Boys ti Champions League.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>*West Ham - Man Utd: 20h Ch nht 19/9, trn VnExpress</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"Rio, mt ln na cc bn bit y, i khi anh y bnh lun v nhng iu m anh y khng thc s nm r. Trong tnh hung , l ra trng ti phi pht th vng Christopher Martins khi cu ta ko ng Nemanja Matic. Bruno Fernandes v Cristiano Ronaldo u l nhng cu th giu tinh thn cnh tranh. H ng ln trong mt khong thi gian ngn v ht ln vi trng ti.  ch l s bc tc khi phi nhn mt s quyt nh ti. Sau , h u ngi xung\", Solskjaer ni trong hp bo trc trn West Ham  vng 5 Ngoi hng Anh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2021/09/19/rona-4306-1632021564.jpg?w=680&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=EjxcLFXhfj8RgFzMxGkAGA\" alt=\"Ronaldo v Fernandes chy ra ng bin cng Solskjaer phn i trng ti. nh: EPA.\"/><figcaption>Ronaldo v Fernandes chy ra ng bin cng HLV Solskjaer phn i trng ti. nh:&nbsp;<em>EPA</em>.</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong trn u Young Boys  lt ra qun Champions League hm gia tun, Martins phi nhn th vng  pht 50. Nu nhn thm th trong tnh hung ko ng Matic  pht 80, tin v i ch nh s phi ri sn v hai i cn bng v lc lng. Trc , Man Utd mt Aaron Wan-Bissaka t pht 35.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi trng ti t chi pht thm th vi Martins, Ronaldo v Fernandes u bc xc. C hai - vn  ri sn tm pht trc  - u bt dy v chy ra phn i cng Solskjaer. Tuy nhin, trong chng trnh bnh lun, Ferdinand coi hnh ng ca Ronaldo l&nbsp;<a href=\"https://vnexpress.net/ferdinand-khong-muon-ronaldo-thay-solskjaer-chi-dao-4357419.html\">ch o cc cu th</a>&nbsp;thay HLV. Cu trung v ngi Anh cn ni: \"Nu ti l HLV, thnh tht m ni, ti s bo Ronaldo ngi xung\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HLV Solskjaer gii thch thm: \"\"Trong khu vc ch o ch c mt ngi c tham gia,  l ti, Michael Carrick, Mick Phelan, hoc Kieran McKenna. Hnh ng ca Ronaldo v Fernandes ch l bt pht, khi cu th i phng l ra phi nhn th vng th hai. Ti khng c vn  g vi vic h th hin cm xc v sau  quay li ch ngi. N khng ging nh Ronaldo ang ch o cc cu th\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Do thi u hn ngi trong hai phn ba thi gian, Young Boys chi ln lt v&nbsp;<a href=\"https://vnexpress.net/young-boys-2-1-man-utd-4356603.html\">ngc dng</a>&nbsp;bng hai bn ca Ngamaleu pht 66 v Siebatcheu pht 90+5. Trc , Ronaldo m t s cho Man Utd pht 13.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>y khng phi l ln u tin Ronaldo gy tranh ci v hnh ng trong khu vc dnh cho HLV. Trong trn chung kt Euro 2016, sau khi chn thng ri sn, anh lin tc ng ln h ho cc ng i, bn cnh HLV Fernando Santos.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Solskjaer: \'Ronaldo khng ch o cu th Man Utd\'', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'solskjaer-ronaldo-khong-chi-dao-cau-thu-man-utd', '', '', '2021-09-22 22:10:47', '2021-09-22 22:10:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress_581/?p=37', 0, 'post', '', 0),
